Ex-Big Brother Naija ‘Double Wahala’ housemate, Nina, has lost her father to the cold hands of death. Nina made it to the top five during the ‘Double Wahalac season and was all over the news during the show in 2018 because of her cozy relationship with another housemate, Miracle Ikechchukwu who emerged winner of that season. She took to her Twitter page on Tuesday to announce the passing away of her father while sharing a write up that had ” R.I.P Dad’ She said: ‘Can’t hold this Anymore….. it’s too much for me to handle.’ Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.